t_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_2,1_2&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; width=&#8221;90%&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;31px|auto||-2px||&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;6px||6px||true|&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|||2%|false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; text_font=&#8221;|300|||||||&#8221; link_text_color=&#8221;#572a53&#8243; header_font=&#8221;Montserrat|300|||||||&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;0px||&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||0px&#8221; header_font_size_tablet=&#8221;28px&#8221; header_font_size_phone=&#8221;24px&#8221; header_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ol>\n<li>S\u00f3lo puede ingresar a la cl\u00ednica la persona que ser\u00e1 atendida.<\/li>\n<li>Los acompa\u00f1antes deben esperar afuera.<\/li>\n<li>Menores de edad deben ser acompa\u00f1ados por una adulto responsable.<\/li>\n<li>Los pacientes deben usar en todo momento una mascarilla y\/o escudo facial que cubra nariz y boca.<\/li>\n<li>Antes de ingresar a la sala de espera, debe desinfectar sus zapatos en los elementos dispuestos para esto.<\/li>\n<li>Al ingresar a la cl\u00ednica, el paciente debe lavarse las manos; tambi\u00e9n debe hacerlo antes de retirarse.<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; custom_padding=&#8221;|2%|||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; text_font=&#8221;|300|||||||&#8221; link_text_color=&#8221;#572a53&#8243; header_font=&#8221;Montserrat|300|||||||&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;0px||&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||0px&#8221; header_font_size_tablet=&#8221;28px&#8221; header_font_size_phone=&#8221;24px&#8221; header_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>7. Debe respetarse el distanciamiento m\u00ednimo de 1 metro.<br \/> 8. El paciente debe llenar un Cuestionario COVID.<br \/> 9. El paciente debe firmar un consentimiento Informado antes de la atenci\u00f3n.<br \/> 10. Se registrar\u00e1 la temperatura del paciente.<br \/> 11. El paciente debe enjuagarse con una soluci\u00f3n desinfectante antes de la atenci\u00f3n.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; width=&#8221;90%&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;6px||6px||true|&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_text _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; text_font=&#8221;|300|||||||&#8221; link_text_color=&#8221;#572a53&#8243; header_font=&#8221;Montserrat|300|||||||&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;0px||&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||0px&#8221; header_font_size_tablet=&#8221;28px&#8221; header_font_size_phone=&#8221;24px&#8221; header_font_size_last_edited=&#8221;on|phone&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;]<\/p>\n<ol><\/ol>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>LOS PACIENTES QUE NO RESPETEN ESTOS PROTOCOLOS, NO SER\u00c1N ATENDIDOS.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][et_pb_row use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;1&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; width=&#8221;90%&#8221; max_width=&#8221;100%&#8221; module_alignment=&#8221;center&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;35px||0px||false|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;4_4&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.15&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;http